"title": "7505: Jews, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7505",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A post-exilic designation for descendants of the people from the kingdom of Judah and also for adherents to their religion from other nations. The term is used extensively in the NT where it has a variety of nuances.</p>\n<h2>Early use of the term ``Jews''</h2>\n<h3>Pre-exilic and exilic use</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:11-Jer40:12\">JER 40:11–40:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:12\">JER 32:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:8-Jer34:9\">JER 34:8–34:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:19\">JER 38:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:15\">JER 40:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:3\">JER 41:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:8-Jer43:9\">JER 43:8–43:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:1\">JER 44:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:26-Jer44:27\">JER 44:26–44:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:28-Jer52:30\">JER 52:28–52:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:8-Dan3:12\">DAN 3:8–3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Used of the citizens of the province of Judah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:1\">EZR 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:23\">EZR 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:5\">EZR 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:7-Ezra6:8\">EZR 6:7–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:14\">EZR 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:16\">NEH 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:1-Neh4:2\">NEH 4:1–4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:12\">NEH 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:6-Neh5:8\">NEH 5:6–5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:17\">NEH 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:5-Neh6:7\">NEH 6:5–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:23\">ZEC 8:23</a></p>\n<h3>Used of the descendants of the exiles from the southern kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:5\">EST 2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:11-Ezra4:12\">EZR 4:11–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:12-Ezra7:20\">EZR 7:12–7:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:1-Esth3:6\">EST 3:1–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:13\">EST 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:3\">EST 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:12-Esth4:14\">EST 4:12–4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:12-Esth6:13\">EST 6:12–6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:5-Esth8:13\">EST 8:5–8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:1-Esth9:3\">EST 9:1–9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:30-Esth9:31\">EST 9:30–9:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth10:3\">EST 10:3</a></p>\n<h2>NT use of the term ``Jews''</h2>\n<h3>Jewish people in general</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:3\">MRK 7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:15\">MAT 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:3\">LUK 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:6\">JHN 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:9\">JHN 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:19-John4:22\">JHN 4:19–4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31-John8:32\">JHN 8:31–8:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:18-John11:19\">JHN 11:18–11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:31-John11:33\">JHN 11:31–11:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:45\">JHN 11:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:9-John12:11\">JHN 12:9–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:20\">JHN 18:20</a></p>\n<h3>Those Jewish leaders who were hostile to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:31\">JHN 19:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:18-John2:20\">JHN 2:18–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:1-John5:18\">JHN 5:1–5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35-John6:42\">JHN 6:35–6:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:1\">JHN 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:11-John7:15\">JHN 7:11–7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:48-John8:59\">JHN 8:48–8:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1-John9:34\">JHN 9:1–9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:22-John10:33\">JHN 10:22–10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:12-John18:14\">JHN 18:12–18:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:28-John18:31\">JHN 18:28–18:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38\">JHN 19:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19\">JHN 20:19</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as ``king of the Jews''</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:37\">MAT 27:37</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:26\">MRK 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:38\">LUK 23:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:19-John19:21\">JHN 19:19–19:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:1-Matt2:2\">MAT 2:1–2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:11\">MAT 27:11</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:2\">MRK 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:33\">JHN 18:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27-Matt27:31\">MAT 27:27–27:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:16-Mark15:20\">MRK 15:16–15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:1-John19:6\">JHN 19:1–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:6-Mark15:14\">MRK 15:6–15:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:38-John18:40\">JHN 18:38–18:40</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel first preached to the Jews</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:19\">ACT 11:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:16-Rom10:21\">ROM 10:16–10:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:41\">ACT 2:1–2:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:23-Acts10:48\">ACT 10:23–10:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:14-Acts13:43\">ACT 13:14–13:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16\">ROM 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:8-Rom15:9\">ROM 15:8–15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:7-Gal2:9\">GAL 2:7–2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Opposition of certain Jews to the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:19\">ACT 20:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8-Acts6:14\">ACT 6:8–6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:23-Acts9:25\">ACT 9:23–9:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:28-Acts9:30\">ACT 9:28–9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:1-Acts12:3\">ACT 12:1–12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:44-Acts13:45\">ACT 13:44–13:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:49-Acts13:50\">ACT 13:49–13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:1-Acts14:6\">ACT 14:1–14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19\">ACT 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:4-Acts17:9\">ACT 17:4–17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:13\">ACT 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:1-Acts18:6\">ACT 18:1–18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12-Acts18:17\">ACT 18:12–18:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:3\">ACT 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:25\">2CO 11:23–11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:27-Acts21:36\">ACT 21:27–21:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:12-Acts23:15\">ACT 23:12–23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:1-Acts24:9\">ACT 24:1–24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:1-Acts25:7\">ACT 25:1–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:19-Acts26:21\">ACT 26:19–26:21</a></p>\n<h2>Believers described as Jews and Gentiles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">ACT 6:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:20-Acts21:21\">ACT 21:20–21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:39\">ACT 21:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:1-Acts22:3\">ACT 22:1–22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:23-Rom9:24\">ROM 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:22-1Cor1:24\">1CO 1:22–1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jews and Gentiles equal in Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25-Rom11:32\">ROM 11:25–11:32</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:26-Gal3:29\">GAL 3:26–3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:27-Rom3:30\">ROM 3:27–3:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:12-Rom10:13\">ROM 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12-1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:12–12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:11\">COL 3:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jews and Gentiles equally in need of salvation</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:1-Rom3:20\">ROM 3:1–3:20</a></p>",
